Ounrsus Christi fidelibus ad quos presens scriptum per- venerit, Johannes Masoall, de Chart, juxta Sutton Valance, in Comitatu Kancie, husbandmen, unus filiorum Roberti Marcell, defuncti-Salutem in domino.
